Bundled Example Data
--------------------

This repository includes small example datasets solely for testing, examples,
and reproducibility of the tutorial figures. These data are third-party
research products and are not relicensed as PyDoppler3D source code.

V834 Cen
~~~~~~~~

Path: pydoppler3d/test_data/v834cen

The V834 Cen spectra and configuration files were taken from the doptomog
archive distributed through CDS catalogue J/A+A/595/A47:

  https://cdsarc.cds.unistra.fr/ftp/J/A+A/595/A47/

Please cite:

  Kotze, E. J., Potter, S. B., & McBride, V. A. 2016,
  Astronomy & Astrophysics, 595, A47.

The archived doptomog package states that its program source is distributed
under the GNU General Public License. The spectra are retained here with their
original provenance for example use; users should consult the CDS archive and
the original paper before redistributing or using them in published analysis.

U Gem
~~~~~

Path: pydoppler3d/test_data/ugem99

The U Gem spectra are included as a compatibility example matching the classic
PyDoppler tutorial data layout.

Please cite:

  Echevarria, J., de la Fuente, E., & Costero, R. 2007,
